OL,3,C'He said the roof was crumbling':
OL,4,CBuilder scams homeowners out of over
OL,5,C#100,000
OL,7,FA pensioner was told by a cowboy
OL,8,Fbuilder her roof could collapse at any
OL,9,Fmoment if she did not send him #2,500
OL,10,Fvia bank transfer.
OL,12,FStewart Langton turned up at the door
OL,13,Fof 82-year-old Lynn Hall in Wesham, ,
OL,14,Fpromising to fix a small leak for "no
OL,15,Fmore than #100".
OL,17,FWhile Lynn had no reason to worry at
OL,18,Ffirst, this was the start of a ruse
OL,19,Fthat Langton had used to scam
OL,20,Fhomeowners out of more than #200,000.
