OL,7,FLynn had noticed the leak in her
OL,8,Fbedroom, and had struggled to find a
OL,9,Ftradesman to fix it.
OL,11,FShe said: "I'd been calling everyone
OL,12,Fand leaving messages but couldn't find
OL,13,Fanyone to fix it
OL,15,F"Then just as it was going dark, this
OL,16,Fman came and said he was a roofer. I
OL,17,Fwas so pleased."
OL,19,FLynn showed Langton round to the back
OL,20,Fof her house and was delighted when he
OL,21,Fsaid he could fix the leak.
