OL,7,FLynn said: "He said it will be #30 -
OL,8,For might even be #100, as though that
OL,9,Fwas the most it could possibly be. He
OL,10,Fsaid he would be back tomorrow."
OL,12,FLangton returned to her home on
OL,13,FPrincess Avenue the next day with
OL,14,Fanother man. The pair put up ladders
OL,15,Fand went to inspect the leak.
OL,17,FLynn said: "He said, 'it will all need
OL,18,Fdoing - the batons are rotted' and he
OL,19,Fthrew a piece of damp wood down to the
OL,20,Fground."
