OL,7,FLangton said the roof was in a
OL,8,Fdangerous state and it could collapse
OL,9,Fat any point overnight. He asked Mrs
OL,10,FHall to make a bank transfer for
OL,11,F#2,500 to secure her home.
OL,13,FLynn said: "I am not too savvy at
OL,14,Fthings like internet banking.
OL,16,F"It seemed a lot he was asking for a
OL,17,Fquarter of the roof. As they were
OL,18,Flooking they were picking the tiles up
OL,19,Foff the roof, saying they were
OL,20,Fcrumbling.
