OL,3,C'He said the roof was crumbling':
OL,4,CBuilder scams homeowners out of over
OL,5,C#100,000
OL,7,F"There was a lad on the roof, nowhere
OL,8,Fnear where the leak was, and Langton
OL,9,Fjust kept going on about this bank
OL,10,Ftransfer.
OL,12,F"It was bad weather and I was really
OL,13,Fworried about the roof coming in. I
OL,14,Fgathered up all the cash I had in the
OL,15,Fhouse, which was #495, which I gave
OL,16,Fhim to buy materials."
OL,18,FBefore leaving, Langton gave her #15
OL,19,Fback as he did not want to "leave her
OL,20,Fpenniless".
