OL,3,C'He said the roof was crumbling':
OL,4,CBuilder scams homeowners out of over
OL,5,C#100,000
OL,7,FHe continued to pressure Lynn into
OL,8,Fsending more money, claiming the full
OL,9,Froof needed to be replaced at a cost
OL,10,Fof #15,000.
OL,12,FLynn said: "I expected him to get in
OL,13,Fthe van and go and get materials but
OL,14,Fhe wasn't going anywhere.
OL,16,F"He just said the roof was crumbling
OL,17,Fand it would cost #7,500 to replace
OL,18,Fone half. To do the whole thing, which
OL,19,Fis what I would have wanted, would
OL,20,Fhave been #15,000.
