OL,3,C'He said the roof was crumbling':
OL,4,CBuilder scams homeowners out of over
OL,5,C#100,000
OL,7,F"In my mind, I was thinking 'give him
OL,8,Fthe money quick and get it done'. I
OL,9,Fwas panicking.
OL,11,F"He kept going on and on about this
OL,12,Fbank transfer. In the end, I said,
OL,13,F'leave it with me and I'll do it
OL,14,Ftomorrow.'"
OL,16,FThe next day, Lynn left the house on
OL,17,Fher mobility scooter to go to a local
OL,18,Fclub. When she arrived, she spoke to a
OL,19,Ffriend who put her in touch with a
OL,20,Freputable builder.
