OL,3,C'He said the roof was crumbling':
OL,4,CBuilder scams homeowners out of over
OL,5,C#100,000
OL,7,FWhen the builder checked Lynn's roof,
OL,8,Fhe said there were just two tiles
OL,9,Fwhich needed replacing.
OL,11,FLynn said: "He showed me there was
OL,12,Fnothing wrong with it."
OL,14,FLynn was not the only victim of
OL,15,FStewart Langton. Between 2022 and
OL,16,F2024, Langton conned 10 homeowners out
OL,17,Fof more than #200,000 for work that
OL,18,Fdid not need to be done, or was done
OL,19,Fto a poor standard.
