OL,3,C'He said the roof was crumbling':
OL,4,CBuilder scams homeowners out of over
OL,5,C#100,000
OL,7,FTrading Standards launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation after receiving a number
OL,9,Fof complaints that customers had been
OL,10,Fquoted low rates for work, only for
OL,11,Fprices to be ramped up once the job
OL,12,Fhad started.
OL,14,FWork was left unfinished and customers
OL,15,Fwere told workers would walk off the
OL,16,Fjob if large amounts of money were not
OL,17,Fpaid immediately.
