OL,7,FLangton, of Whalley Lane, Blackpool,
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for four years and
OL,9,Fthree months after he pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto carrying out a fraudulent business.
OL,12,FHe has also been handed a 10 year
OL,13,Fcriminal behaviour order, banning him
OL,14,Ffrom working on people's homes.
